## 🗺️ Framework Selection Guide

Use this decision tree to pick the right agentic framework:

```
Does your workflow have complex state, loops, or dependencies?
    │
    ├── YES ──► Do you need real-time, high-performance execution?
    │               ├── YES ──► LangGraph
    │               └── NO  ──► LangGraph (still preferred for complex graphs)
    │
    └── NO  ──► Do you need multiple agents to debate and refine together?
                    ├── YES ──► AutoGen
                    └── NO  ──► Do you need role-based team execution?
                                    ├── YES ──► CrewAI
                                    └── NO  ──► Simple LLM call may suffice
```

